Debug log configuration

Setup → Debug Logs → New Trace Flag on your user. The default SFDC_DevConsole debug level won't show flow internals — create a custom one:

Category	Level	What it unlocks
Apex Code	FINEST	USER_DEBUG, CODE_UNIT_STARTED/FINISHED
Workflow	FINER	all FLOW_* entries — this is the one people miss
Validation	INFO	VALIDATION_RULE, VALIDATION_PASS/FAIL
Database	INFO	DML_BEGIN/END, SOQL_EXECUTE_*
Apex Profiling	FINE	CUMULATIVE_LIMIT_USAGE block
System	DEBUG	

Flow logging lives under Workflow, not a category called "Flow". At INFO you get interview start/end only; FINER gives you element-by-element; FINEST adds every value assignment.
